synopsis.text: Academy's Team Fawn, long aspiring to stand alongside the revered Team Rabbit, finds their opportunity knocking as the formidable GDF initiates a fresh assault. Catch the thrilling action in an all-new 'episode 25', set to air following a rebroadcast of the original 2013 TV series, commencing in July. This special episode serves as a bridge, seamlessly connecting the series to the upcoming Majestic Prince film, promising an engaging viewing experience for both new and returning fans.
